config SUNXI_DECD
	tristate "Allwinner H713 Display Engine Controller (decd)"
	depends on OF && ARCH_SUNXI
	select RESET_CONTROLLER
	help
	  Display engine controller driver for the Allwinner H713 SoC.

	  Provides frame submission, VSync-driven scheduling, DMA-BUF
	  import/export, and dma-fence synchronization for the AFBD
	  (ARM Frame Buffer Decoder) display path.

	  Required for video output on the HY310 projector platform.
	  Depends on sunxi_tvtop for shared display-top resource management.

	  Based on reverse engineering of stock decd.ko from H713 SDK.

	  If unsure, say M.
